[package]

[dependencies.serde]

[package]
name = "conrod_core"
version = "0.63.0"
authors = [ "Mitchell Nordine <mitchell.nordine@gmail.com>", "Sven Nilsen <bvssvni@gmail.com>",]
keywords = [ "ui", "widgets", "gui", "interface", "graphics",]
description = "An easy-to-use, 100% Rust, extensible 2D GUI library."
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
readme = "../README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/pistondevelopers/conrod.git"
homepage = "https://github.com/pistondevelopers/conrod"
documentation = "http://docs.piston.rs/conrod/conrod/"
categories = [ "gui",]

[features]
stdweb = [ "instant/stdweb",]

[dependencies]
daggy = "0.5"
fnv = "1.0"
num = "0.2"
pistoncore-input = "0.24"
instant = "0.1"
copypasta = "0.8"

[dependencies.conrod_derive]
path = "../conrod_derive"
version = "0.63"

[dependencies.rusttype]
version = "0.7"
features = [ "gpu_cache",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true

[package]
name = "conrod_derive"
version = "0.63.0"
authors = [ "mitchmindtree <mitchell.nordine@gmail.com>",]
description = "A crate providing procedural macros for the conrod library"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
keywords = [ "conrod", "gui", "derive", "procedural", "macro",]
repository = "https://github.com/pistondevelopers/conrod.git"
homepage = "https://github.com/pistondevelopers/conrod"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "0.4.2"
quote = "0.6"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "0.15"
features = [ "extra-traits", "full",]

[package]
name = "conrod_winit"
version = "0.63.0"
authors = [ "Mitchell Nordine <mitchell.nordine@gmail.com>", "Sven Nilsen <bvssvni@gmail.com>",]
keywords = [ "ui", "widgets", "gui", "interface", "graphics",]
description = "An easy-to-use, 100% Rust, extensible 2D GUI library."
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
readme = "../../README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/pistondevelopers/conrod.git"
homepage = "https://github.com/pistondevelopers/conrod"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/conrod"
categories = [ "gui",]

[lib]
name = "conrod_winit"
path = "./src/lib.rs"

[dependencies]

[package]
name = "egui_wgpu_backend"

authors = [ "Nils Hasenbanck <nils@hasenbanck.de>",]
edition = "2018"
description = "Backend code to use egui with wgpu."
homepage = "https://github.com/hasenbanck/egui_wgpu_backend"
repository = "https://github.com/hasenbanck/egui_wgpu_backend"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
readme = "README.md"

[features]
default = []
web = []

[dependencies]
epi = "0.12"
wgpu = "0.8"
bytemuck = "1.5"

[package]
name = "fluent"
description = "A localization system designed to unleash the entire expressive power of\nnatural language translations.\n"
version = "0.16.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Zibi Braniecki <gandalf@mozilla.com>", "Staś Małolepszy <stas@mozilla.com>",]
homepage = "http://www.projectfluent.org"
license = "Apache-2.0/MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/projectfluent/fluent-rs"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "localization", "l10n", "i18n", "intl", "internationalization",]
categories = [ "localization", "internationalization",]
include = [ "src/**/*", "benches/*.rs", "Cargo.toml", "README.md", "LICENSE-APACHE", "LICENSE-MIT",]

[dependencies]
unic-langid = "0.9"

[dependencies.fluent-bundle]
version = "0.15"
path = "../fluent-bundle"

[dependencies.fluent-pseudo]
version = "0.3"
optional = true

[[bench]]
name = "resolver"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "resolver_iai"
harness = false

[package]
name = "fluent-bundle"
description = "A localization system designed to unleash the entire expressive power of\nnatural language translations.\n"
version = "0.15.2"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Zibi Braniecki <gandalf@mozilla.com>", "Staś Małolepszy <stas@mozilla.com>",]

[features]

[dependencies.fluent-syntax]

[dev-dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dev-dependencies.unic-langid]
version = "0.9"
features = [ "macros",]

[[bench]]
name = "parser"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "parser_iai"
harness = false

[[bin]]
name = "parser"

[[bin]]
name = "update_fixtures"
path = "src/bin/update_fixtures.rs"

[[test]]
name = "parser_fixtures"
path = "tests/parser_fixtures.rs"

[package]
name = "fluent-syntax"
description = "Parser/Serializer tools for Fluent Syntax.\n"
version = "0.11.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Zibi Braniecki <gandalf@mozilla.com>", "Staś Małolepszy <stas@mozilla.com>",]
homepage = "http://www.projectfluent.org"
license = "Apache-2.0/MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/projectfluent/fluent-rs"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "localization", "l10n", "i18n", "intl", "internationalization",]
categories = [ "localization", "internationalization",]
include = [ "src/**/*", "benches/*.rs", "Cargo.toml", "README.md", "LICENSE-APACHE", "LICENSE-MIT",]

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0"

[dev-dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0"
glob = "0.3"
criterion = "0.3"
iai = "0.1"

[features]
default = []
json = [ "serde", "serde_json",]
all-benchmarks = []

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[package]
